original: Brette, Nils Verner, landsfiskal, Åmål, f. 21/9/99 i Örebro av tandl. G. A. F. Karlsson o. Vilma Molin. G. 29 m. Karin Wetterwik. Barn: Anders f. 30, Kerstin 34, Carl-Axel 35. — Lands fiskals ex. 25. Tf. landsfiskal i Högsäter 31, ord. där 36, landsfiskal i Amål sed. 41.
translated: Brette, Nils Verner, district prosecutor, born September 21, 1899 in Örebro to dentist G. A. F. Karlsson and Vilma Molin. Married Karin Wetterwik in 1929. Children: Anders (born 1930), Kerstin (born 1934), and Carl-Axel (born 1935). Passed the district prosecutor exam in 1925. Acting district prosecutor in Högsäter in 1931, appointed there in 1936, district prosecutor in Åmål from 1941 onwards.
